--------------
1. DESCRIPTION
--------------

The Tk::DataTree class is a derivate of Tk::Tree intended
for displaying arbitrary data structures.

---------------
2. INSTALLATION
---------------

Installation of the Tk::DataTree module follows the standard
Perl Way and should not be harder than:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install

Note that you may need to become superuser to 'make install'.

If you're building the module under Windows, you may need to use a
different make program, such as 'nmake', instead of 'make'.

---------------
3. DEPENDENCIES
---------------

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Tk (obviously)

